>
<ul>
<li>Network Security Type: WPA2 Enterprise</li>
<li>Required Security: 802.1x EAP</li>
<li>Encryption Type: AES</li>
<li>Network Authentication Method: PEAP, MSCHAPv2</li>
<li>Authentication after selecting MSCHAPv2: BYU-Idaho Username and Password</li>
</ul>
<p>Here is the basic information needed to  configure most devices to access <strong>BYU-Idaho email</strong>.</p>
<ul>
<li>Email Account Type: Microsoft Exchange/ Corporate</li>
<li>Domain for Employees: BYUI for Employees</li>
<li>Domain for Students: leave "Domain" blank</li>
<li>Server for Employees: owa.byui.edu</li>
<li>Server for Students: ~https://sn2prd0106.outlook.com (found when they login to their BYU-Idaho email through outlook.com or through the my.byui Email tab).</li>
<li>Note on "Server for Students": the above-provided information is NOT the complete web address on purpose. Anything past "...outlook.com" is not required on other devices for the Server field. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Select the Phones menu, Tablets menu or continue to the password reset instructions.</p>
